name: basic_sorting_practice
author: 金策浙江省杭州学军中学
summary: This paper is titled 'Basic Sorting Algorithm Practice Problems' and appears to be a collection of exercise problems focused on fundamental sorting techniques. However, the provided text does not contain any actual content related to sorting algorithms. Instead, it contains fragments from other papers in Chinese (or another East Asian language) discussing topics such as number theory functions (multiplicative functions), Dirichlet convolution, Möbius inversion, network flows, linear programming, and graph theory. The section specifically attributed to Jin Ce from Hangzhou Xuejun High School, which should discuss basic sorting, is entirely missing or corrupted in the provided text.
